headline.print_headline: Defending Champ Nishikori Wins in Memphis Debut
headline.main: Defending Champ Nishikori Wins in Memphis Debut

lead_paragraph: Defending champion Kei Nishikori of Japan beat Benjamin Becker of Germany 6-4, 6-4 on Wednesday night in the U.S. National Indoor Tennis Championships.
